ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you have any interest in public policy or American politics, this is a class you should take.

The course is demanding and worthwhile. The course has a high return on investment. The more you engage with readings and prioritize time each week for the course, the better experience you will have.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The final paper requirement for this course has greatly improved my research and writing abilities over the course of this semester.
The course contributed significantly to my dissertation/research.
The research project at the end is an excellent opportunity to advance one's dissertation / publishing aims. I was appreciative that the requirements were loose so that I could do what I wanted.
